This is the master branch. 

All the stable codes are here.

========================================================================================

Install Prerequsite for MongoDB C++ Driver

> apt-get install build-essential scons libboost-dev libboost-program-options-dev libboost-thread-dev libboost-filesystem-dev
> cd lib/mongo; scons

Aug. 9th

Please install apr-1.0 and apr-util-1.0 packages

> apt-get install libaprutil1-dev libapr1-dev

compiling add link lib: -lapr-1 -laprutil-1

now the memorypool.hh & memorypool.cc are still the same with previous version.
memorypool_apr.hh & memorypool_apr.cc are added.

